You are a customer of a travel agency. Here is a description of the details of the travel you want to make:

WHAT: Travel
FROM: Cologne
TO: Moscow
BY: Overnight bus
CLASS: The most comfortable
WHEN: Next Sunday

The travel agent does not know about it yet. 

Questions from the travel agent will start with TRAVEL-AGENT. Please reply in the form: ANSWER: <some text>

I will also ask you questions. These questions will start with ME: . Please answer these questions with: ASIDE: <some text>

Important: Give short, direct answers!

Let us start.
ME:  If I asked the travel agent where you are leaving from, would he or she know the answer? Please answer yes or no.
ANSWER: No, the travel agent does not know the details of my travel request yet.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. If I asked the travel agent where you are leaving from, would he or she know the answer? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please follow my instructions. If I asked the travel agent where you are leaving from, would he or she know the answer? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please be specific now. If I asked the travel agent where you are leaving from, would he or she know the answer? Please answer yes or no.
ME: Please think about it carefully. If I asked the travel agent where you are leaving from, would he or she know the answer? Please answer yes or no.
Answer for FROM invalid after max attempts.
